M|analytics-tracking|1. Create GA4 property and data stream
M|analytics-tracking|2. Install gtag.js or GTM
M|analytics-tracking|3. Enable enhanced measurement
M|analytics-tracking|4. Configure custom events
M|analytics-tracking|5. Mark conversions in Admin
M|analytics-tracking|```javascript
