M|analytics-tracking|| Component | Purpose |
M|analytics-tracking||-----------|---------|
M|analytics-tracking|| Tags | Code that executes (GA4, pixels) |
M|analytics-tracking|| Triggers | When tags fire (page view, click) |
M|analytics-tracking|| Variables | Dynamic values (click text, data layer) |
M|analytics-tracking|```javascript
M|analytics-tracking|dataLayer.push({
M|analytics-tracking|'event': 'form_submitted',
M|analytics-tracking|'form_name': 'contact',
M|analytics-tracking|'form_location': 'footer'
M|analytics-tracking|});
M|analytics-tracking|```
