M|analytics-tracking|- Lowercase everything
M|analytics-tracking|- Use underscores or hyphens consistently
M|analytics-tracking|- Be specific but concise: `blog_footer_cta`, not `cta1`
M|analytics-tracking|- doc all UTMs in a spreadsheet
